tiralabra.datastructures

Class Tree<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tiralabra.datastructures.Tree<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Class of the elements in the tree.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TreeMap

    public class Tree<E>
extends Object
    Binary red-black search tree. On insertion and removal the tree uses self-balancing techniques to keep the height of the tree logarithmic in respect to the amount of elements.
    Author:
    Pavel
